[{"text": " I'm finished, guys.", "start": 0.0, "duration": 0.99}, {"text": "I'm finished.", "start": 0.99, "duration": 1.53}, {"text": "Now this is all about making\nmyself credible in your eyes", "start": 2.52, "duration": 2.44}, {"text": "again.", "start": 4.96, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "And I'm going to do\nthat by admitting", "start": 5.76, "duration": 2.07}, {"text": "that evolution is a lie.", "start": 7.83, "duration": 3.87}, {"text": " Goddamn, you Mac.", "start": 11.7, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": " Yes, please do, Mac.", "start": 13.22, "duration": 2.56}, {"text": " Now as you can see, this\nis the evolution meter.", "start": 15.78, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "And I've put God, the\ncreator of everything,", "start": 18.03, "duration": 2.55}, {"text": "on the right side and\nevolution on the left.", "start": 20.58, "duration": 3.46}, {"text": "I've went ahead and put\nyou guys all on the fence", "start": 24.04, "duration": 1.76}, {"text": "because of course, you're going\nto hear out all my arguments.", "start": 25.8, "duration": 1.23}, {"text": " Actually, no.", "start": 27.03, "duration": 1.33}, {"text": " Let's start where\nI would start.", "start": 28.36, "duration": 1.79}, {"text": "MAC: No matter.", "start": 30.15, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": "I'm righteous.", "start": 31.1, "duration": 1.11}, {"text": "I'm not going to\nstand here, present", "start": 32.21, "duration": 2.17}, {"text": "some egghead scientific\nargument based on fact.", "start": 34.38, "duration": 4.5}, {"text": "I'm just a regular dude.", "start": 38.88, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "I like to drink beer, you know?", "start": 40.68, "duration": 1.47}, {"text": "I love my family.", "start": 42.15, "duration": 1.13}, {"text": "Rock, flag, and eagle.", "start": 43.28, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "Right, Charlie?", "start": 44.13, "duration": 1.14}, {"text": " He's got a point.", "start": 45.27, "duration": 1.11}, {"text": " No, he doesn't.", "start": 46.38, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " What?", "start": 47.18, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "MAC: You see, Charlie,\nthese liberals", "start": 47.98, "duration": 1.49}, {"text": "are trying to\nassassinate my character.", "start": 49.47, "duration": 2.025}, {"text": "And I can't change their mind.", "start": 51.495, "duration": 1.975}, {"text": "I won't change my mind\nbecause I don't have to.", "start": 53.47, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "Because I'm an American.", "start": 55.79, "duration": 2.06}, {"text": "I won't change my\nmind on anything,", "start": 57.85, "duration": 1.58}, {"text": "regardless of the facts\nthat are set out before me.", "start": 59.43, "duration": 3.51}, {"text": "I'm dug in.", "start": 62.94, "duration": 1.799}, {"text": "And I'll never change.", "start": 64.739, "duration": 1.981}, {"text": " Mac, look.", "start": 66.72, "duration": 0.84}, {"text": "You're wasting our time.", "start": 67.56, "duration": 1.45}, {"text": "You're not going to get us\nto not believe in evolution.", "start": 69.01, "duration": 3.23}, {"text": " And why is that?", "start": 72.24, "duration": 1.02}, {"text": " Because the smartest\nscientists in the entire world", "start": 73.26, "duration": 2.85}, {"text": "all agree that it's real.", "start": 76.11, "duration": 2.76}, {"text": " I'm glad you brought that up.", "start": 78.87, "duration": 1.47}, {"text": "Because Mr. Reynolds,\nscience is a liar sometimes.", "start": 80.34, "duration": 5.9}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 86.24, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " Oh, boy.", "start": 87.04, "duration": 0.98}, {"text": " This is Aristotle,\nthought to be", "start": 88.02, "duration": 3.9}, {"text": "the smartest man on the planet.", "start": 91.92, "duration": 1.78}, {"text": "He believed that the\nearth was the center", "start": 93.7, "duration": 1.94}, {"text": "of the universe and\neverybody believed", "start": 95.64, "duration": 1.8}, {"text": "him because he was so smart.", "start": 97.44, "duration": 2.25}, {"text": "Until another smartest\nguy came around, Galileo.", "start": 99.69, "duration": 4.32}, {"text": "And he disproved\nthat theory, making", "start": 104.01, "duration": 1.83}, {"text": "Aristotle and everybody else\non earth look like a bitch.", "start": 105.84, "duration": 4.63}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 110.47, "duration": 1.16}, {"text": " Of course, Galileo\nthen thought comets", "start": 111.63, "duration": 3.34}, {"text": "were an optical illusion.", "start": 114.97, "duration": 1.83}, {"text": "And there's no way that the moon\ncould cause the ocean's tides.", "start": 116.8, "duration": 4.44}, {"text": "Everybody believed that\nbecause he was so smart.", "start": 121.24, "duration": 2.55}, {"text": "He was also wrong, making him\nand everyone else on earth", "start": 123.79, "duration": 4.299}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 128.089, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Look like a bitch again.", "start": 128.889, "duration": 2.041}, {"text": "And then, best of\nall, Sir Isaac Newton", "start": 130.93, "duration": 3.27}, {"text": "gets born and blows everybody's\nnips off with his big brains.", "start": 134.2, "duration": 3.86}, {"text": "Of course, he also thought\nhe could turn metal into gold", "start": 138.06, "duration": 2.17}, {"text": "and died eating mercury, making\nhim yet another stupid bitch.", "start": 140.23, "duration": 5.4}, {"text": "[DRUM]", "start": 145.63, "duration": 2.0}, {"text": "Are you seeing a pattern?", "start": 147.63, "duration": 1.77}, {"text": " No.", "start": 149.4, "duration": 0.95}, {"text": " Mr. Reynolds, these\nwere all the smartest", "start": 150.35, "duration": 2.86}, {"text": "scientists on the planet.", "start": 153.21, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "Only problem is they\nkept being wrong.", "start": 155.31, "duration": 3.38}, {"text": "Sometimes.", "start": 158.69, "duration": 1.337}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 160.027, "duration": 1.133}, {"text": " This is insane, you fool.", "start": 161.16, "duration": 2.13}, {"text": " I'm a fool because I have\nmore faith in the saints that", "start": 163.29, "duration": 2.34}, {"text": "wrote the Bible?", "start": 165.63, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": " Yeah, because you just read\nthe words of a bunch of guys", "start": 166.68, "duration": 3.18}, {"text": "that you never met, and you\njust take it on faith that", "start": 169.86, "duration": 3.51}, {"text": "everything they wrote was true.", "start": 173.37, "duration": 1.29}, {"text": " Um.", "start": 174.66, "duration": 0.84}, {"text": "And what makes you\nthink what you're", "start": 175.5, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "scientists are writing is any\nmore truer than my saints?", "start": 176.7, "duration": 2.18}, {"text": " Because there are volumes of\nproven data, numbers, you know,", "start": 178.88, "duration": 5.05}, {"text": "figures.", "start": 183.93, "duration": 0.99}, {"text": "Th-- There are fossil records.", "start": 184.92, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": " Oh, fossil records.", "start": 187.02, "duration": 1.23}, {"text": "Ah.", "start": 188.25, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "I didn't even think\nabout the fossil records.", "start": 189.05, "duration": 1.33}, {"text": "I guess I'll concede.", "start": 190.38, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Oh wait, one more thing\nbefore I do, Mr. Reynolds.", "start": 191.18, "duration": 3.1}, {"text": "Have you seen these\nfossil records?", "start": 194.28, "duration": 2.32}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 196.6, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " Have I--", "start": 197.4, "duration": 0.96}, {"text": "Huh?", "start": 198.36, "duration": 1.17}, {"text": " Have you pored through\nthe data yourself?", "start": 199.53, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "The numbers, the figures.", "start": 201.63, "duration": 2.2}, {"text": " Well, no.", "start": 203.83, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "I'm-- No.", "start": 204.63, "duration": 1.32}, {"text": " Oh, interesting.", "start": 205.95, "duration": 1.95}, {"text": "So let me get this\nstraight, Mr. Reynolds.", "start": 207.9, "duration": 2.19}, {"text": "You get your information\nfrom a book written", "start": 210.09, "duration": 1.89}, {"text": "by men you've never met.", "start": 211.98, "duration": 2.34}, {"text": "And you take their words as\ntruth based on a willingness", "start": 214.32, "duration": 2.52}, {"text": "to believe, a desire to\naccept, a leap of f--", "start": 216.84, "duration": 4.84}, {"text": "Dare I say it?", "start": 221.68, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Ha.", "start": 222.48, "duration": 1.43}, {"text": "Faith?", "start": 223.91, "duration": 0.804}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 224.714, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " Oh, come--", "start": 225.514, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Come on.", "start": 226.314, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "Look, I, I mean, I don't\neven know how I'm supposed", "start": 227.114, "duration": 1.836}, {"text": "to respond to that, like--", "start": 228.95, "duration": 1.27}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 230.22, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " I get lied.", "start": 231.02, "duration": 1.48}, {"text": " That is a--", "start": 232.5, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "that's a false e-- equivalency.", "start": 233.3, "duration": 1.44}, {"text": "[GONG]", "start": 234.74, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " Just answer the\nquestion, Mr. Reynolds.", "start": 235.54, "duration": 3.43}, {"text": " Sure.", "start": 238.97, "duration": 0.84}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 239.81, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "OK.", "start": 240.61, "duration": 2.71}, {"text": " I rest my case.", "start": 243.32, "duration": 0.93}, {"text": "[BELL RINGING]", "start": 244.25, "duration": 0.91}, {"text": " Well, that got me.", "start": 245.16, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "[MUSIC PLAYING] I\nthink he [INAUDIBLE]..", "start": 245.96, "duration": 1.52}, {"text": "- You want me to--\n- Put me up.", "start": 247.48, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": " Yeah, all right", "start": 248.68, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " What?", "start": 249.48, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": " Well, we're\ngoing on the fence.", "start": 250.28, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": "I mean, there's a\nshadow of a doubt.", "start": 251.48, "duration": 1.2}, {"text": " You actually don't believe\nin evolution anymore?", "start": 252.68, "duration": 2.26}, {"text": " I don't know.", "start": 254.94, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "He created a reasonable doubt.", "start": 255.74, "duration": 1.49}, {"text": "He makes you sound\nlike a stupid ah--", "start": 257.23, "duration": 1.66}, {"text": "science bitch.", "start": 258.89, "duration": 0.97}, {"text": " Yeah, he got you good.", "start": 259.86, "duration": 1.419}, {"text": " Oh, my god.", "start": 261.279, "duration": 1.951}]